data.value:
The Hackathon Scheduler is a dynamic and interactive software solution designed to streamline the scheduling and management of knockout-style tournaments in hackathons, specifically tailored for **Capture The Flag (CTF)** competitions. The application automates the process of scheduling matches, tracking results, and ensuring fair competition between teams.
Features: - Team Registration: Users can easily input and manage team details, including team names, members, and ranks. - Tournament Scheduling: Automatically schedules matches between teams based on their ranks, with a knockout structure progressing through several rounds. - Match Management: Allows users to track match status (Scheduled or Completed) and record the outcome of each match. - User-Friendly Interface: Simple and intuitive GUI to navigate through the tournament stages and track the progress of matches. - Randomized Scheduling: Ensures fairness by randomly matching teams in each round while respecting the initial ranking for the first round. - Real-Time Updates: View match results and tournament progression instantly after each match is completed.
Technologies Used: - NET Framework: Built using C# and the .NET Framework for rich desktop applications. - Windows Forms: Developed with a Windows Forms interface to provide a simple yet functional GUI. - Custom Data Structures: Utilizes custom classes and data structures to efficiently store team and match data, avoiding reliance on third-party libraries.
Goal of the Project: This project aims to provide an automated system for managing competitive events like Capture The Flag and Showdown tournaments, ensuring a smooth experience for both participants and event organizers. It reduces the administrative overhead of manually scheduling and tracking tournament matches and results, making the competition more enjoyable and efficient.
Team Members: - Basim Raza - Munawar Masood - Abdullah Asim
Contact & Support: For additional information, feedback, or support, you can contact us at: support@hackathonscheduler.com
